### ==========================================
### 1. 商户 (Merchant) 流程
### ==========================================

### 1.1 注册商户
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "merchant_01",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "merchant"
}

### 1.2 商户登录 (⚠️ 复制返回的 token 用于 test_hotel.http 和 test_rooms.http)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "merchant_01",
  "password": "123456"
}

